gst-plugins-base: gst-plugins-base (GStreamer Base Plugins)
gst-plugins-base:
gst-plugins-base: This is the basic set of plugins for GStreamer.
gst-plugins-base:
gst-plugins-base: It contains a set of reference plugins, base classes for other 
gst-plugins-base: plugins, and helper libraries. This module is kept up-to-date 
gst-plugins-base: together with the core developments. This module contains elements for:
gst-plugins-base: device plugins, codecs, audio processing, visualisation, and video 
gst-plugins-base: processing.
